{"tid":2493462,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"如果LSE LLB同HKU LLB比offer你","createTime":"2021-04-18T02:47:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T08:34:54.000Z","uid":248054,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0ca6d5eaaab3f7f3e82eb7b4835c3ecc7e3185df","tid":2493462,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T02:47:50.000Z","msg":"你會揀邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔考慮學費問題"},{"pid":"ece82ffc30f2c0e24e9341a6148f363706e1606c","tid":2493462,"uid":248054,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T02:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmThTP9CDEwZ7U2oqkqdwi22P54ja111mC9VcfVw7wMZqa?filename=3FVp4Zm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3FVp4Zm.jpg&h=7f8f6a1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b663bba25cc44db6e8f118f4bfffd5f709e197a8","tid":2493462,"uid":248054,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T02:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmS9ZXMuBg3pKp3BHpjh6hN2vwk3QbgiHDy8ZADRRLfnb6?filename=2GDi9q5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GDi9q5.jpg&h=7917a47d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfbea5296f53f2f2f3eddee667389a6d3f22997e","tid":2493462,"uid":366201,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T02:50:35.000Z","msg":"係XGU <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再出過post 啦～"},{"pid":"a044baa5efee2538b9a40e2ba80219162fec3e43","tid":2493462,"uid":248054,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T02:51:27.000Z","msg":"香港大学法学院是最富盛名的学院。<br />\n<br />\n我们可以从香港每年的高考状元的选择就可以看出（香港的同学是评级制，每年会有数位状元），基本都会选择HKU的法学专业或是医学专业。<br />\n<br />\n✌就业发展情况同学们的发展都是蛮好的。可以在各种外所、内所香港分所做paralegal，然后可能会去美国读bar获取后续的晋升空间或是回到内所做高年级律师。现在内所发展的也很好，同学们也有直接到红圈所、精品所发展，大家共同向着财富自如努力奋斗。另外也有同学抱有学术理想，继续读博。<br />\n<br />\n✌就读心得体会香港留学是我不后悔的选择。这里有国际化的视野，和魂牵梦绕的传统文化，这里可以看到法律与资本运作的接近完美的结合，可以领略中华文化和西方理念碰撞的火花。作为法律人，在香港，你可以看到民众对法律的敬畏与信仰，对法律人的信任和尊敬。我想不管是对自己的职业发展还是自我价值的提升，香港可以为法学留学生提供足以期许的未来。"},{"pid":"d2a4a639b4eb2d9a898ef189c8f2ec3b3fcc8744","tid":2493462,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T02:52:55.000Z","msg":"假設性問題一律唔答"},{"pid":"c5a03fab6e4d8681760c936267716c52cc37840f","tid":2493462,"uid":248054,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T02:53:04.000Z","msg":"LSE Law is very pleased to announce that we have once again been ranked in the top-ten universities worldwide for Law by the highly respected Times Higher Education World University Rankings, alongside other leading institutions in both the UK and USA. This is testimony to the quality of both our teaching and research. The 2020 Times Higher Education World University Rankings table for law uses the same trusted and rigorous performance indicators as overall THE World University Rankings, recalibrated to suit the individual field."},{"pid":"5f3404b8072f1558ec40d832764e5ae79e836802","tid":2493462,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfbea5296f53f2f2f3eddee667389a6d3f22997e","tid":2493462,"uid":366201,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T02:50:35.000Z","msg":"係XGU <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再出過post 啦～"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T02:55:30.000Z","msg":"XGU LLB 同LSE LLB<br />\n你會點揀"},{"pid":"a88e711b4145e592ea8767f35d17d23698089624","tid":2493462,"uid":247211,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T02:57:02.000Z","msg":"問得黎都戇鳩<br />\n香港只有一間大學叫暴大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2946251934e5a642b0c49cce9b59db9120726377","tid":2493462,"uid":42283,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:01:08.000Z","msg":"一定係LSE"},{"pid":"a0